
A fullstack developer is someone who is proficient in both frontend and backend programming languages and framework, i.e someone who is both a frontend and a backend
web developer. Frontend end web developers majorly deal with how a website is displayed while backend development involves the creation, update and collection of 
data received from frontend webdevelopment in order to manipulate it to produce a desired output.

Tools used by Fullstack deveopers include
1.Text editor eg Vscode, nano.
2.Frontend client side tools such as Angular, Bootstrap, Php,SQL, HTML, CSS, Javascript and so on.
3.Backend tools such as Django, NodeJS ASP.net etc.
4.Git services and clients.
